Question 2
Run the Command to create the Dockerfile

docker build -t adhoc:shreya https://github.com/redashu/summer2020dockertest.git

Use this command to tag the image

docker tag adhoc:shreya shreya/adhoc:shreya

Then use this to login to docker

docker login

Enter you username and password
Run the command to push to docker hub

docker push shreya/adhoc:shreya

The image shreya/adhoc:shreya has be uploaded to Docker Hub
